745a4d6d666666","tid":12994,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打學咗幾多年？平時彈咩類型多？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就跟老師學咗6年，但好懶唔係日日練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意tarrega同villa-lobos<br />\n<br />\n呢排老師教la catedral，自己得閒就彈緊villa-lobos 嘅幾首choro</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六年已經玩la catedral <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我玩左九年啦 最鐘意巴哈同villa lobos <br />\nVilla lobos 嗰堆prelude 同etude真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfd510970d775a7c133a65c3ed0c110ffa067e7","tid":12994,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打學咗幾多年？平時彈咩類型多？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就跟老師學咗6年，但好懶唔係日日練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意tarrega同villa-lobos<br />\n<br />\n呢排老師教la catedral，自己得閒就彈緊villa-lobos 嘅幾首choro</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六年已經玩la catedral <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我玩左九年啦 最鐘意巴哈同villa lobos <br />\nVilla lobos 嗰堆prelude 同etude真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學緊first movement同second movement咋，third movement太難，冇可能彈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己好多時彈到一pat屎咁<br />\n不過始終都係當興趣，又年紀大先學，當興趣自娛下減下壓，彈到啲簡單歌都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打鍾意邊個演奏家？我就最鍾意segovia、julian bream同楊雪霏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b102e3bb4fcc78cb256d2934b3cc1261f92ead","tid":12994,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打學咗幾多年？平時彈咩類型多？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就跟老師學咗6年，但好懶唔係日日練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意tarrega同villa-lobos<br />\n<br />\n呢排老師教la catedral，自己得閒就彈緊villa-lobos 嘅幾首choro</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六年已經玩la catedral <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我玩左九年啦 最鐘意巴哈同villa lobos <br />\nVilla lobos 嗰堆prelude 同etude真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學緊first movement同second movement咋，third movement太難，冇可能彈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己好多時彈到一pat屎咁<br />\n不過始終都係當興趣，又年紀大先學，當興趣自娛下減下壓，彈到啲簡單歌都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打鍾意邊個演奏家？我就最鍾意segovia、julian bream同楊雪霏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都鐘意julian bream 佢同john Williams 啲二重奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外Pepe Romeo 都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb38c56fcca70fc04eec250058fef76ca934793","tid":12994,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打學咗幾多年？平時彈咩類型多？<br />\n<br />\n我自己就跟老師學咗6年，但好懶唔係日日練琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鍾意tarrega同villa-lobos<br />\n<br />\n呢排老師教la catedral，自己得閒就彈緊villa-lobos 嘅幾首choro</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n六年已經玩la catedral <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我玩左九年啦 最鐘意巴哈同villa lobos <br />\nVilla lobos 嗰堆prelude 同etude真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n學緊first movement同second movement咋，third movement太難，冇可能彈到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得自己好多時彈到一pat屎咁<br />\n不過始終都係當興趣，又年紀大先學，當興趣自娛下減下壓，彈到啲簡單歌都好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打鍾意邊個演奏家？我就最鍾意segovia、julian bream同楊雪霏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都鐘意julian bream 佢同john Williams 啲二重奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n另外Pepe Romeo 都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前買咗julian bream套cd collection，好正<br />\n平時唔特別好john williams（雖然係令人好準確嘅演奏家）<br />\n但佢同bream二重奏個concert真係好正<br />\n有debussy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\npepe romero係咪幾年前有嚟香港？你嗰陣有冇去？<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪偏見，我就唔多鍾意嗰個milos karadaglic<br />\n啲tremolo好似「done」出嚟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解佢好似成日嚟香港表演<br />\n（不過我唔係專業，應該係唔識欣賞啫）"},{"pid":"a8263f48cca9b512f7f2ebcb8055710d64b8d811","tid":12994,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:56:47.000Z","msg":"始終milos後生 同Williams bream pepe 呢啲大師比起黎 真係爭啲 聽佢啲recording都唔係太好聽"},{"pid":"8ef1231671f07609059f7f252ab2ec8c13011e64","tid":12994,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"好耐先彈得成一首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b97a990fd241487ad3c818e08a8723767713e240","tid":12994,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited