blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要啦，鍾意古典結他嘅聲音都算係同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfingerstyle我都唔多識，巴打講多啲教下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b452d645fad4bbe209d7333e6479d136278b29","tid":12994,"uid":43331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:57:47.000Z","msg":"睇黎真係無咩人玩古典結他 成朝都無咩人入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b950d243160f7ceeef44ca342e3d6287f42bc685","tid":12994,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:55:11.000Z","msg":"古典結他真係算冷門<br />\n始終好多人一聽到話彈結他都係諗彈唱民謠或者電結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8138b1b39c153f4c800aab1ae1a4a55fa4bbc6c0","tid":12994,"uid":16156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"我身邊有班高手，已經彈哂la catedral,koyunbaba,vl etude,arabe &amp; alhambra，sor folia varation,english suite,1006a prelude果類，我就得個葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7413ef89cffe1dfd1f2c7b53c32ab85d9b309d","tid":12994,"uid":16156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:21:02.000Z","msg":"早排有冇聽pierri 同barrueco,超正，仲好過dr黎果次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb1412e091245f7a2ab98f3ac2d47fed7ce63dde","tid":12994,"uid":42214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我身邊有班高手，已經彈哂la catedral,koyunbaba,vl etude,arabe &amp;amp; alhambra，sor folia varation,english suite,1006a prelude果類，我就得個葡萄<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔使葡萄嘅，音樂係一生嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n能夠一直彈落去都可以好開心<br />\n<br />\n而且都唔一定係高難度嘅先好聽<br />\n有好多簡簡單單都好好聽<br />\n最緊要自己鍾意同適合自己<br />\n<br />\n呢位巴打自己彈開啲咩呢？"},{"pid":"c9916505aefcff3476e1346741a1e7c0077fe743","tid":12994,"uid":12748,"li